Package: httsnap
Title: An http DSL
Description: Easy 'http' for 'R'. Provides functions for building http queries,
    including query parameters, body requests, paging, authentication, and
    various curl options.
Version: 0.0.6.9000
Authors@R: person("Scott", "Chamberlain", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "myrmecocystus@gmail.com")
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    httr
Imports:
    curl,
    jsonlite,
    magrittr,
    lazyeval,
    whisker,
    R6
Suggests:
    testthat
